    <name>Line Merger</name>
    
    <shortDescription>
        This node merges a collection of line to a single line
    </shortDescription>
    
    <fullDescription>
        <intro>Merges a collection of linear components to form maximal-length linestrings. Details are available 
        <a href="http://javadox.com/com.vividsolutions/jts/1.13/com/vividsolutions/jts/operation/linemerge/LineMerger.html">here</a>.
        This is a row-wise operation.</intro>
        
        
